# Cursor Rules

# Project Documentation
- Look to folder [Project documentation](../docs/)

## Coding Standards
- Use Laravel (backend) + React/Inertia (frontend) best practices SOLID, DRY, KISS
- Follow PSR-12 (PHP) and ESLint (JS/TS)
- Use Tailwind for styling
- Use [Development Guidelines](../docs/development-guidelines.md)

## Git & Commits
- Use conventional commits (feat, fix, docs, refactor, chore)
- Commit frequently, PRs should be < 300 lines

## Cursor Usage
- Always check `/docs` docs before coding
- Respect ADR decisions in `/docs/decisions`
- Follow tasks in `.cursor/tasks/` for specific changes

## Testing
- Unit tests by Pest testing framework required for backend logic
- Cypress for E2E frontend tests
